<style>
    .overSelect {
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
    }

    .Scroll::-webkit-scrollbar {
        width: 6px;
        background-color: #cccccc;
    }

    .Scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
        background-color: #18a7c9;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

        .Scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background-color: #18a7c9;
            border: 1px solid #333333;
        }

        .Scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:active {
            background-color: #18a7c9;
            border: 1px solid #333333;

   <script>
       $(document).ready(function () {
           $("#pricebuy").css("display", "block");
           $("#pricerent1").css("display", "none");

           $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdFinalTransType").val("Buy");

           $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_ddlType").change(function () {
               var transtype = $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_ddlType option:selected").val();
               $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdFinalTransType").val(transtype);

               if (transtype == "Buy") {
                   $("#pricerent").val('');
                   $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblRentprice").val('');
                   $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblRentprice").text('');

                   $("#pricebuy").css("display", "block");
                   $("#pricerent1").css("display", "none");
                   PriceRange();
               }
               if (transtype == "Rent") {
                   $("#price-input").val('');
                   $("#price-input").text('');
                   $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblBuyprice").val('');
                   $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblBuyprice").text('');
                   $("#pricebuy").css("display", "none");
                   $("#pricerent1").css("display", "block");
                   PriceRangerent();
               }

           });

           $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_aid").click(function () {

               var i = 0;
               myval();
               if ($("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_txtLocation").val() == "" || $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HDLocationId").val() == "") {

                   $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_txtLocation").css({ 'border-color': 'red' });
                   $("#ErrorMessage").text("Invalid Location");
                   $("#ErrorMessage").css({ "color": "red" });
                   i = 1;
               }

               var proptype = $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanelHDPropertyGroup").val();

               if (proptype == "") {
                   $("#ddlPropertyType").css({ "border-color": "red" });
                   $("#errorPropertyType").text("Enter Property Type");
                   i = 1;
               }
               // alert(i);                    
               if (i == 1) {
                   return false;
               }
               else {
                   return true;
               }

           });

       });

       function PriceRange() {

           var from = parseFloat($("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdFromValue").val());
           var to = parseFloat($("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdtoValue").val());
           var trans = $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HDtranstype").val();
           var $priceSlider = $("#price-input");
           var val1 = parseFloat(from);
           var val2 = parseFloat(to);
           var val3 = trans;

           var stepvalue;
           if (val3 == "SALE") {
               stepvalue = parseInt("10000");
           }
           if (val3 == "RENT") {
               stepvalue = parseInt("1000");
           }

           $("#price-input").val(val1 + ";" + val2);

           if ($priceSlider.length > 0) {

               $priceSlider.slider({
                   from: val1,
                   to: val2,
                   step: stepvalue,
                   round: 5,
                   values: [val1, val2],
                   format: { format: 'Rs ' + '<span datavalue>###,###</span>', locale: 'en' },
                   change: function (event, ui) {
                       $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblBuyprice").val(ui.value);
                       $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblBuyprice").text(ui.value);

                       calculate();
                   },
                   slide: function (event, ui) {
                       $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblBuyprice").val(ui.value);
                       $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblBuyprice").text(ui.value);

                   }
               });
           }


       }
       function myval() {
           var j_v1 = $("#pricebuy .jslider-value span[datavalue]:first").text()
           var j_v2 = $("#pricebuy .jslider-value span[datavalue]:last").text()
           var j_v3 = $("#pricerent1 .jslider-value span[datavalue]:first").text()
           var j_v4 = $("#pricerent1 .jslider-value span[datavalue]:last").text()
           $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdFinalBuyMinValue").val(j_v1);
           $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdFinalBuyMaxValue").val(j_v2);
           $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdFinalRentMinValue").val(j_v3);
           $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdFinalRentMaxValue").val(j_v4);
       }
       function PriceRangerent() {
           //  alert("priceRent");
           var from = parseFloat($("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdFromValuerent").val());
           var to = parseFloat($("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HdtoValuerent").val());
           var trans = $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_HDtranstyperent").val()
           var $priceSlider = $("#pricerent");
           var val1 = parseFloat(from);
           var val2 = parseFloat(to);
           var val3 = trans;
           var stepvalue;
           if (val3 == "SALE") {
               stepvalue = parseInt("10000");
           }
           if (val3 == "RENT") {
               stepvalue = parseInt("1000");
           }

           $("#pricerent").val(val1 + ";" + val2);

           if ($priceSlider.length > 0) {

               $priceSlider.slider({
                   from: val1,
                   to: val2,
                   step: stepvalue,
                   round: 5,
                   values: [val1, val2],
                   format: { format: 'Rs ' + '<span datavalue>###,###</span>', locale: 'en' },
                   change: function (event, ui) {
                       $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblRentprice").val(ui.value);
                       $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblRentprice").text(ui.value);
                       // alert($("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblRentprice").text());
                       calculate();
                   },
                   slide: function (event, ui) {
                       $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblRentprice").val(ui.value);
                       $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblRentprice").text(ui.value);
                       // alert($("#ContentPlaceHolder1_SearchPanel_lblRentprice").text());
                   }
               });
           }

       }

</script>

    <script>
        jQuery(function () {
            $(".menu-icon").click(function (e) {
                $(".main-menu-wrapper").slideToggle(500);
            })
        });
        //crmlink
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $("#crmlink").click(function (e) {
                $("#divpopupdashboard, .mypopup-container").hide();
            });
            // Mobile Manu
            $("span[click-search-filter]").click(function (e) {
                $("body").toggleClass("filter");
            });
            $("div[ui-overlay]").click(function (e) {
                $("body").toggleClass("filter");
            });
            // Refine search
            $("span[click-refine-search]").click(function (e) {
                $("body").toggleClass("refine-search-list");
            });
            $("div[hide-refine-search]").click(function (e) {
                $("body").toggleClass("refine-search-list");
            });
        });

        function setControls() {
            var usercode = '';
            if (usercode == "") {
                $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNameProperty1").val('');
                $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNameProperty1").css({ 'border-color': '' });
                $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtTelphoneProperty").val('');
                $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtTelphoneProperty").css({ 'border-color': '' });
                $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtEmailProperty1").val('');
                $("#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtEmailProperty1").css({ 'border-color': '' });
                $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNameProperty1').removeAttr("disabled");
                $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtTelphoneProperty').removeAttr("disabled");
                $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtEmailProperty1').removeAttr("disabled");
            }
            else {
                $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtNameProperty1').attr("disabled", "disabled");
                $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtTelphoneProperty').attr("disabled", "disabled");
                $('#ContentPlaceHolder1_txtEmailProperty1').attr("disabled", "disabled");
            }
        }
    </script>

            function ShowPopup(modal) {
                $(".popup, .popup-container").show();
                $(".popup-container").fadeIn(500, function () {
                    $(".popup").animate({ right: "0" }, 500, function () {
                    });
                });
            }

            function RestrictSpace() {
                if (event.keyCode == 32) {
                    return false;
                }

        <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function () {
                //$('.reg').hide();
                //$('.myprofile').hide();
                $("body").removeAttr("style");

                $("div[data-city-overlay]").on("click", function () {
                    $(".AllCityContainer, div[data-city-overlay]").toggleClass("hide");
                });
                $(".userCityHandler").on("click", function () {
                    $(".CityArrow").toggleClass("hide");
                    $(".AllCityContainer, div[data-city-overlay]").toggleClass("hide");
                });


                var usercode = ''
                if (usercode.length > 0) {
                    $('.reg').css("display", "none");
                    $('.myprofile').css("display", "block");
                }
                else {
                    $('.myprofile').css("display", "none");
                    $('.reg').css("display", "block");

                    if ($("#hdnShowSigninPopup").val() == "ShowPop") {
                        ShowSignIn();
                        $("#lblLoginError").text("Login Fail..., Please try again.");
                    }
                }


            });
        </script>
        <script>
            $(document).ready(function () {
                $("#Submit").click(function () {

                    var usercode = ''
                    if (usercode.length > 0) {
                        $('.reg').css("display", "none");
                        $('.myprofile').css("display", "block");
                    }
                    else {
                        $('.reg').css("display", "block");
                        $('.myprofile').css("display", "none");
                    }
                });

                $("#logout").click(function () {
                    $('.reg').css("display", "block");
                    $('.myprofile').css("display", "none");
                });


            });
        </script>
        <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function () {

                $("#btnCloseSub").click(function (e) {
                    HideSubDialog();
                    e.preventDefault();

                });

                $("#overlay").click(function (e) {
                    HideSubDialog();
                });

                $('.form-control').on("keydown", function (event) {
                    if (event.keyCode == 13) {

                        event.preventDefault();
                    }
                });

            });

            $(document).keyup(function (e) {

                if (e.keyCode == 27) {
                    HideSubDialog();
                }   // escape key maps to keycode `27`
            });
            function ShowSubDialog(modal) {
                $("#divaskOverlay").show();
                $("#dialogSub").fadeIn(300);

                if (modal) {
                    $("#divaskOverlay").bind("click");
                }
                else {
                    $("#divaskOverlay").click(function (e) {
                        HideSubDialog();
                    });
                }
            }

            function HideSubDialog() {
                $("#divaskOverlay").hide();
                $("#dialogSub").fadeOut(300);
            }
        </script>
        <script type="text/javascript" defer="defer">

                    buttonWidth: 240,
                    maxHeight: 300
                });

            });
        </script>
        <script>

            function CheckAndOpen() {
                var usercode = '';
                //alert(usercode);
                if (usercode == "") {
                    //data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signin"
                    //$("#postproperty").attr("data-toggle", "modal");
                    //$("#postproperty").attr("data-target", "#signin");
                    ShowSignIn();
                }
                else {
                    $("#postproperty").attr("href", "Post-Your-Property");
                }
            }

            function ValidateEmail(email) {
                var expr = /^([\w-\.]+)@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.)|(([\w-]+\.)+))([a-zA-Z]{2,4}|[0-9]{1,3})(\]?)$/;
                return expr.test(email);
            }

            $(document).ready(function () {

                $("#Submit").click(function (e) {
                    
                    var expr = /^([\w-\.]+)@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.)|(([\w-]+\.)+))([a-zA-Z]{2,4}|[0-9]{1,3})(\]?)$/;
                    if ($("#txtEmail").val() != "") {
                        if (!expr.test($("#txtEmail").val())) {
                            $("#txtEmail").css({ "border-color": "red" });
                            $("#lblEmailerror").text("Please Enter valid email");
                            return false;
                        }
                        else {
                            ShowSubDialog(true);
                            var param = {
                                EmailId: $("#txtEmail").val()
                            };

                            $.ajax({

                                url: "DefaultOld.aspx/InsertSubscription",

                                data: JSON.stringify(param),

                                dataType: "json",

                                type: "POST",

                                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",

                                dataFilter: function (data) { return data; },

                                success: function (data) {
                                    if (data.d != "") {
                                        //alert('1');
                                        $("#txtEmail").css({ "border-color": "red" });
                                        //ShowSubDialog(true);
                                        //$("#lblEmailerror").text("Email Id Already Subscribed");
                                        $("#Span1").text('Email Id already subscribed');
                                        $("#Subthank").text('');
                                    }
                                    else {
                                        //alert('2');
                                        $("#txtEmail").css({ "border-color": "" });
                                        $("#lblEmailerror").text("");
                                        $("#Span1").text('Your Subscription is submitted successfully. You will soon receive revert from hindustanproperty.com');
                                        $("#txtEmail").val("");
                                    }
                                }
                            });
                            return false;
                        }
                    }
                    else {
                        $("#txtEmail").css({ "border-color": "red" });
                        $("#lblEmailerror").text("Please Enter Email Id");
                        return false;
                    }
                });


                $("#txtEmail").blur(function () {
                    var expr = /^([\w-\.]+)@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.)|(([\w-]+\.)+))([a-zA-Z]{2,4}|[0-9]{1,3})(\]?)$/;
                    if ($("#txtEmail").val() == "") {
                        $("#txtEmail").css({ "border-color": "red" });
                        $("#lblEmailerror").text("Please Enter Email Id");
                    }
                    else {
                        $("#txtEmail").css({ "border-color": "" });
                        $("#lblEmailerror").text("");
                    }
                    if ($("#txtEmail").val() != "") {
                        if (!expr.test($("#txtEmail").val())) {
                            $("#txtEmail").css({ "border-color": "red" });
                            $("#lblEmailerror").text("Please Enter valid email");
                            return false;
                        }
                        else {
                            $("#txtEmail").css({ "border-color": "" });
                            $("#lblEmailerror").text("");
                            return true;
                        }
                    }

                });

            });

        </script>

        <script>

            //crmlink
            $(document).ready(function () {
                $(".menu-icon").click(function (e) {
                    
                    $(".main-menu-wrapper").slideToggle(5000);
                })
                $(".closeModal").click(function (e) {
                    $("#RegisPop").click();
                });


                $("#crmlink").click(function (e) {
                    
                    $("#divpopupdashboard, .mypopup-container").hide();
                });

                $("a[data-click-city]").on("click", function () {
                    
                    //$(".CityArrow").toggleClass("hide");
                    $(".AllCityContainer, div[data-city-overlay]").toggleClass("hide");
                });

                $("#CloseAllCity").click(function (e) {
                    $(".AllCityContainer, div[data-city-overlay]").toggleClass("hide");
                });
                $(".userCityHandler").on("click", function () {
                    $(".CityArrow").toggleClass("hide");
                    $(".AllCityContainer").toggleClass("hide");
                });
                //$("ul[data-city='metro']").hover CityArrow
                $("ul[data-city='metro'] > li").hover(function () {
                    var title = $(this).children().attr('title');
                    $("div[data-city-image=''] > div").css({ "z-index": "0" })
                    $('div[city-img="' + title + '"]').css({ "z-index": "9" });
                    //console.log('div[city-img="' + title + '"]');
                    //console.log($("div[data-city-image=''] > div").css({"z-index":"11"}));
                });

                $(".select_city > span").on("click", function (e) {
                    $(".city_container").slideToggle(500);
                });

                $(".rhtStickyBtn").on("click", function (event) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $("body").toggleClass("Requirement_animate");
                    $("#VerificationReq").css("display", "none");
                    $("#maindiv").css("display", "block");
                    $("#thanksdivReq").css("display", "none");
                    ShowPostRequirement();
                });
                $("a.Requirement-close, div[data-overlay-form]").on("click", function (event) {
                    event.preventDefault();
                    $("body").toggleClass("Requirement_animate");
                });

                if ($(window).width() < 1024) {
                    
                } else {
                   
                    $("ul[role='byeRent'] > li").on("click", function (event) {
                        // event.preventDefault();
                        $("ul[role='byeRent'] > li").removeClass("active");
                        $(this).toggleClass("active");
                    });
                }

            });

        </script>

        <script>
            function ShowSignIn()
            {
                var usercode = ''
                if (usercode.length > 0) {
                   
                }
                else {
                    $("#RegisPop").modal();
                    $("#signup").css("display", "none");
                    $("#VerificationMaster").css("display", "none");
                    $("#DivRegSucsses").css("display", "none");
                    $("#DivForgotMail").css("display", "none");
                    $("#signin").css("display", "block");
                    $("#DivVerification").css("display", "none");
                    CleareSignIn();
                }
            }
            function ShowSignUp() {
                $("#RegisPop").modal();
                $("#signup").css("display", "block");
                $("#VerificationMaster").css("display", "none");
                $("#DivRegSucsses").css("display", "none");
                $("#DivForgotMail").css("display", "none");
                $("#signin").css("display", "none");
                CleareControls();

            }
            function ShowVerification() {
                $("#RegisPop").modal();
                $("#signup").css("display", "none");
                $("#VerificationMaster").css("display", "block");
                $("#DivRegSucsses").css("display", "none");
                $("#DivForgotMail").css("display", "none");
                $("#signin").css("display", "none");

            }
            function ShowRegSucc() {
                $("#RegisPop").modal();
                $("#signup").css("display", "none");
                $("#VerificationMaster").css("display", "none");
                $("#DivRegSucsses").css("display", "block");
                $("#DivForgotMail").css("display", "none");
                $("#signin").css("display", "none");

            }
            function ShowForgetMail() {
                $("#RegisPop").modal();
                $("#signup").css("display", "none");
                $("#VerificationMaster").css("display", "none");
                $("#DivRegSucsses").css("display", "none");
                $("#DivForgotMail").css("display", "block");
                $("#signin").css("display", "none");

            }

            function CleareControls()
            {
                $("#txtUserName").css('border-color', '');
                $("#txtUserName").val("");
                $("#lbluserName").text("");

                $("#txtEmail1").css('border-color', '');
                $("#txtEmail1").val("");
                $("#lblErroeEmail1").text("");

                $("#txtMobileNo").css('border-color', '');
                $("#txtMobileNo").val("");
                $("#lblmobileno").text("");

                $("#txtPassword").css('border-color', '');
                $("#txtPassword").val("");
                $("#lblerrorpassword").text("");

                $("#txtConfirmPass").css('border-color', '');
                $("#txtConfirmPass").val("");
                $("#lblerrorcpwd").text("");
            }

            function CleareSignIn()
            {
                $("#txtLoginUserName").css('border-color', '');
                $("#txtLoginUserName").val("");
                $("#lblLoginUserError").text("");

                $("#txtLogPassword").css('border-color', '');
                $("#txtLogPassword").val("");
                $("#lblLoginPasswordError").text("");
                $("#lblLoginError").text("");
            }
        </script>
